com.shopify.buy.model

Class CartLineItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shopify.buy.model.LineItem
      • com.shopify.buy.model.CartLineItem

  • public class CartLineItem
extends LineItem
    CartLineItem is a subclass of LineItem that extends the object by exposing the ProductVariant that the line item was initialized with. Note that this object is only used for a Cart and line item objects on a Checkout are represented by LineItem objects that only contain the variant ID (if created from a ProductVariant).
